name: devsession
description: The JavaScript runtime is single threaded and therefore does not truly support cuncurrency. However, it does support the appearance of concurrency with combination of the [Event loop](https://nodejs.org/en/docs/guides/event-loop-timers-and-nexttick) runtime and built-in [Asynchronous functions](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/async_function).
